            <h3>KGNU’s Annual Plant Sale - June 4th</h3>
            </mj-text>
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section>

      <mj-column>
        <mj-text>
          It’s almost time for one of our favorite fundraisers of the year! KGNU’s Annual Plant Sale will be held on Sunday, June 4th from 9 am to 3 pm at KGNU’s Boulder headquarters located at 4700 Walnut Street. We will have a variety of plants, veggie starts, garden items, flats of herbs, perennials and more! We will also be accepting plant donations May 17-28th. Questions? Email sarah@kgnu.org or call 303.515.4522.
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-color="#E0E0E0" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>

    <mj-section>
      <mj-column  width="100%">
      <mj-text>
        <h4>Pizza with a Purpose! May 8-May 14th* - Support KGNU!</h4>
        <p>KGNU has partnered with California Pizza Kitchen for "Pizza with a Purpose!" I mean, who doesn’t love to indulge in some pizza pie every now and then? Well, you can support KGNU at any of the California Pizza Kitchen locations listed below between <strong>May 8-14th</strong>. Bring in this flier {{ link to flier, kgnu site }} or just tell your server at California Pizza Kitchen that you would like to donate 20% of your bill to KGNU!</p>

        <p>It’s that easy to enjoy some pizza and support KGNU.</p>

        <p><strong>Where and When: At these California Pizza Kitchen locations May 8-14th*</strong></p>

        <ul>
          <li>Broomfield - FlatIron Crossing, 1 W. Flatiron Cir., #1120, Broomfield, CO 80021</li>
          <li>Boulder - 1711 29th Street #1180 Boulder, CO 80301</li>
          <li>Park Meadows - 8343 S Park Meadows Center Dr, Littleton, CO 80124</li>
          <li>Cherry Creek Shopping Center - 3000 E. First Ave. Sp. 185, Cherry Creek Mall, Denver, CO 80206 *(until until May 13th only)</li>
        </ul>
        <p><em>Click on image for printable version:</em></p>
      </mj-text>
