          <h4>Burritos for a Cause! Illegal Pete’s on Colfax Supports KGNU on June 26th!</h4>
          <p>
            KGNU has partnered with Illegal Pete’s on Colfax in Denver for “Burritos for a Cause!” KGNU DJ, Groove Thief will be DJing from  <strong>5pm - Midnight on June 26th</strong> to party with Illegal Pete’s and KGNU. On this night from 5pm - midnight 50% of your bill will be donated to KGNU if mentioned. KGNU will be taking donations at our booth at the event as well. Eat some delicious Illegal Pete’s in Denver and support KGNU!
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-color="#E0E0E0" />
