          <h4>Bike to Work Day: Have Breakfast at KGNU June 26th!</h4>
          <p>
          <a href="https://communitycycles.org/">Community Cycles</a> has organized more than 60 local businesses in Boulder to host breakfast and bike service stations to serve food and drinks for commuters on Bike to Work Day  <strong>June 26th from 6:30 to 9 a.m.</strong> KGNU is again proud to be of the breakfast stations! Come win tickets to a concert or an annual membership and take a tour of our studios to see how the radio you hear everyday happens. Roll up to our Boulder studios at 4700 Walnut St. for breakfast June 26th.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-color="#E0E0E0" />
      </mj-column>
