      <h4>Save The Date: KGNU's 29th Annual Charles Sawtelle Memorial Mountain Jam at the Gold Hill Inn on July 23rd!</h4>
      <p>
        We’re excited to welcome headliner <a href="http://laurielewis.com/">Laurie Lewis</a> and her  and along with local favorites <a href="http://www.masontownmusic.com/">Mason Town</a> and <a href="https://thunderandrainmusic.com/">Thunder &amp; Rain</a>. Click <a href="http://kgnu.org/cgi-bin/moreinfo.py?Notice=1493484837">here</a> for more information.
      </p>
      </mj-text>
      </mj-column>

