            KGNU’s <a href="http://kgnu.org/cgi-bin/moreinfo.py?Notice=1493486453">Annual Program Guide</a> will be ready to pick up the first week of June at the Boulder station, 4700 Walnut. The electronic version will be posted <a href="https://issuu.com/kgnu">here</a> the first week of June.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
