          <h4>A Call for Records and CDs! KGNU’s Annual CD and Record Sale - Aug 27th</h4>
          <p>KGNU has revived our annual <a href="http://kgnu.org/cgi-bin/moreinfo.py?Notice=1493482022">Record and CD Sale</a>, taking place this year <strong>Sun 8/27 and Fri 9/1</strong> at our Denver home at 700 Kalamath St.</p>

          <p>Please consider making a donation of your gently used audio treasures at either our Boulder or Denver studios during business hours, or call 303-825-5468 or email dave@kgnu.org to arrange a pick-up. Then come to the sale and explore some new-to-you sounds.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
