        <mj-text>
          <h4>New Organizational Memberships!</h4>
          <p>KGNU is a listener supported, volunteer powered community radio station. By becoming an individual, business or nonprofit member of KGNU you will support independent media and receive membership benefits at the same time.</p>

          <p>As a <a href="https://give.kgnu.org/kgnu-nonprofit-membership/">KGNU Nonprofit</a> or <a href="https://give.kgnu.org/small-business-membership/">Small Business Member</a>, your organization will gain significant exposure across the Front Range through KGNU’s on-air, digital, and print media channels. For more information on KGNU’s new organizational membership levels and the benefits you will receive, visit <a href="https://give.kgnu.org">give.kgnu.org</a></p>

          <p>Questions? Email sarah@kgnu.org or call 303.515.4522.</p>
        </mj-text>
